divs: sighting details8\14\2013 5:19am i was driving to work from surprise az, to central phoenix. i stopped at a stop sign on the access road to grand ave. and saw there was a nice cloud formation backed by a colorful sunrise. i often takes pictures of scenes like this, when i can, and since there were no cars behind me this early, i decided to snap one of this view. grand ave runs diagonal (s\e - n\w).i held my phone\camera out of the drivers side window and took the shot facing east at the sunrise. i took two shots and never even reviewed them until a few days later (monday august 19th 2013). i was at home using my phone to view my pics on my tv and that's when i noticed the glowing lights in the sky above the clouds. the tv doesn't have the function to zoom in so i had to look back at my phones screen to zoom in and was in aw at what i was looking at. 6 orbs of light in a circular or oval shape. i'm not sure if they were separate objects or all a part of one object. i live near luke airforce base and see fighter jets all the time but this was definitely not one of them.
Summary: On my way to work, I took a picture of the sunrise. Later discovered the orb formation in my photo.
